title: Developer should create a community campaign
body:
Proposal.

Since Kobe is a community project, developers should create a community campaign to incentivize Kobe community to help to reach out to new projects to create liquidity pools on KobeSwap.  I’ve seen some smaller projects doing this, and it seems to be quite effective and yields some pretty good results over time.. It takes some time for the community to become effective, but once they do the results can be quite amazing.

This way community can help to grow the project while earning rewards.
